## Deployment

- Production server: `49.234.112.108` ‚Äî see `DEPLOYMENT.md`
- Deploy via `deploy/deploy.sh` and `deploy/docker-compose.prod.yml`
- PostgreSQL on port **6541** (existing server instance)

## Workflow

- Run `npm run test:unit` and `npm run test:integration` before commits
- Run `tests/e2e-test.sh` after deploy or full stack start
- After major milestones: commit with descriptive message and push to `origin`
- Match existing code patterns; minimal scope per change

